29
00:01:42,654 --> 00:01:45,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you Mr. Fujiwara of Project D?</b></font>

30
00:01:47,614 --> 00:01:49,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's dishonest and horrible!</b></font>

31
00:02:11,664 --> 00:02:12,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What happened?</b></font>

32
00:02:12,694 --> 00:02:14,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Took the day off today.</b></font>

33
00:02:14,364 --> 00:02:16,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I took another shift for someone else.</b></font>

34
00:02:16,604 --> 00:02:18,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Comp time off, huh?</b></font>

35
00:02:18,664 --> 00:02:21,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How did it go?
You're done with Ibaraki, right?</b></font>

36
00:02:21,864 --> 00:02:23,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did you lose?</b></font>

37
00:02:23,314 --> 00:02:24,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I won.</b></font>

38
00:02:24,304 --> 00:02:27,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then why do you look so gloomy?</b></font>

39
00:02:27,894 --> 00:02:30,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's about something else.</b></font>

40
00:02:34,024 --> 00:02:35,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who is this?</b></font>

41
00:02:36,414 --> 00:02:37,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello?</b></font>

42
00:02:39,624 --> 00:02:43,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, um... it's fine, but hold on.</b></font>

43
00:02:45,724 --> 00:02:46,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's the matter?</b></font>

44
00:02:46,774 --> 00:02:47,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A girl?</b></font>

45
00:02:50,844 --> 00:02:51,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello.</b></font>

46
00:02:52,464 --> 00:02:56,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry for calling you so suddenly.</b></font>

47
00:02:56,224 --> 00:03:00,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanted to apologize to you earlier, but...</b></font>

48
00:03:01,864 --> 00:03:04,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, it's okay.</b></font>

49
00:03:04,154 --> 00:03:06,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How did you get my number?</b></font>

50
00:03:07,304 --> 00:03:12,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I looked up the number for the gas station,
and when I called, an attendant gave me your number.</b></font>

51
00:03:13,224 --> 00:03:14,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see.</b></font>

52
00:03:15,164 --> 00:03:18,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm so sorry for saying such awful things.</b></font>

53
00:03:18,524 --> 00:03:20,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You must be mad at me.</b></font>

54
00:03:21,054 --> 00:03:25,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I'm okay as long
as you know it wasn't me.</b></font>

55
00:03:26,184 --> 00:03:33,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought I should apologize
in person instead of calling you.</b></font>

56
00:03:33,264 --> 00:03:38,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but the days flew by before
I could make time to come visit you.</b></font>

57
00:03:38,394 --> 00:03:40,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm truly sorry.</b></font>

58
00:03:40,014 --> 00:03:41,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll find time to visit you.</b></font>

59
00:03:43,564 --> 00:03:44,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well then.</b></font>

60
00:03:44,904 --> 00:03:48,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um, what about me coming there?</b></font>

61
00:03:49,264 --> 00:03:49,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Eh?</b></font>

62
00:03:50,234 --> 00:03:54,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's if you're okay with it.</b></font>

63
00:03:54,454 --> 00:03:58,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't mind driving
to your neighborhood.</b></font>

64
00:04:00,104 --> 00:04:02,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>W-what am I saying?!</b></font>

65
00:04:04,474 --> 00:04:07,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you sure, really?</b></font>

66
00:04:08,994 --> 00:04:10,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Y-yeah.</b></font>

67
00:04:17,014 --> 00:04:21,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Act 2  [ New Battlefield ]</b></font>

68
00:04:31,544 --> 00:04:33,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you for coming all this way.</b></font>

69
00:04:41,094 --> 00:04:49,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To be honest, I was sort of relieved and glad when I realized that it wasn't you, after showing your picture to Tomoko.</b></font>

70
00:04:51,584 --> 00:04:56,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I saw you for the first time,
you didn't look like a dishonest person.</b></font>

71
00:04:56,214 --> 00:04:59,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But you went pretty far, didn't you?</b></font>

72
00:04:59,364 --> 00:05:02,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got carried away
because I was so furious.</b></font>

73
00:05:03,914 --> 00:05:04,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm really sorry.</b></font>

74
00:05:04,894 --> 00:05:08,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It must have hurt because
I work out in the club.</b></font>

75
00:05:09,464 --> 00:05:10,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you do?</b></font>

76
00:05:11,464 --> 00:05:12,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Golf.</b></font>

77
00:05:12,624 --> 00:05:14,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been practicing since I was little.</b></font>

78
00:05:17,164 --> 00:05:22,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've got training camp and competitions, 
so my summer break is packed with training.</b></font>

79
00:05:23,994 --> 00:05:27,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So I couldn't come to Gunma.</b></font>

80
00:05:27,184 --> 00:05:29,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm glad you came.</b></font>

81
00:05:29,764 --> 00:05:32,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I took my father's suggestion
and started to play golf.</b></font>

82
00:05:32,314 --> 00:05:34,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I skip training, he gets mad.</b></font>

83
00:05:36,634 --> 00:05:39,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That sounds familiar.</b></font>

84
00:05:39,844 --> 00:05:44,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was forced to learn how to
drive since I was in middle school.</b></font>

85
00:05:45,414 --> 00:05:52,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hated it before, and we butted heads a lot, but
I eventually began to drive because I wanted to.</b></font>

86
00:05:53,764 --> 00:05:55,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I understand what you're saying so well.</b></font>

87
00:05:55,894 --> 00:05:58,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I argued with my dad all the time.</b></font>

88
00:05:59,234 --> 00:06:03,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But now golf is a part of my daily life.</b></font>

89
00:06:03,864 --> 00:06:04,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're alike.</b></font>

90
00:06:10,514 --> 00:06:11,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the hell?!</b></font>

91
00:06:11,474 --> 00:06:13,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You went to Saitama to see her today?!</b></font>

92
00:06:14,084 --> 00:06:17,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And what did you talk about?</b></font>

93
00:06:17,264 --> 00:06:18,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nothing really.</b></font>

94
00:06:18,414 --> 00:06:21,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We just had tea in a family
restaurant for about an hour.</b></font>

95
00:06:21,914 --> 00:06:23,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's her name?</b></font>

96
00:06:23,814 --> 00:06:25,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How old is she?</b></font>

97
00:06:25,084 --> 00:06:30,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Her name is Uehara Mika, and she's a year 
younger than us, so she's a senior in high school.</b></font>

98
00:06:30,314 --> 00:06:31,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And what?</b></font>

99
00:06:31,634 --> 00:06:33,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is she taken?</b></font>

100
00:06:33,294 --> 00:06:34,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you going to date her?</b></font>

101
00:06:34,424 --> 00:06:35,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

102
00:06:35,974 --> 00:06:38,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We didn't talk about anything like that.</b></font>

103
00:06:38,454 --> 00:06:39,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not you.</b></font>

104
00:06:39,724 --> 00:06:40,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why not?</b></font>

105
00:06:40,974 --> 00:06:42,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the most important part, isn't it?</b></font>

106
00:06:42,904 --> 00:06:48,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We couldn't talk much in
such a short period of time.</b></font>

107
00:06:48,014 --> 00:06:49,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was really short.</b></font>

108
00:06:50,754 --> 00:06:53,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm gonna say this because it's you.</b></font>

109
00:06:53,494 --> 00:06:58,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think I fell in love with
her the first time I saw her.</b></font>

110
00:07:00,274 --> 00:07:01,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wish I could say that!</b></font>

111
00:07:01,614 --> 00:07:03,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm so envious!</b></font>

112
00:07:03,044 --> 00:07:05,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel awkward.</b></font>

113
00:07:05,864 --> 00:07:09,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know what
to do about this feeling.</b></font>

114
00:07:09,264 --> 00:07:10,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't get it.</b></font>

115
00:07:11,264 --> 00:07:17,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you like her, you have to gather
your courage and make a move.</b></font>

116
00:07:17,944 --> 00:07:22,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But it could be one sided.</b></font>

117
00:07:22,214 --> 00:07:25,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She doesn't necessarily feel the same way.</b></font>

118
00:07:25,984 --> 00:07:29,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sounds awfully timid for a driving genius.</b></font>

119
00:07:29,954 --> 00:07:32,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That has nothing to do with this.</b></font>

120
00:07:33,064 --> 00:07:35,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not very confident.</b></font>

121
00:07:41,314 --> 00:07:46,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll counter Project D with four
carefully planned defensive lines.</b></font>

122
00:07:55,214 --> 00:07:59,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Sidewinder Chief Driver - Hojo Gou</b></font>

123
00:07:55,434 --> 00:08:01,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As a prelude to the battles in Hakone, we'll watch how our opponents race on this mountain path.</b></font>

124
00:07:59,764 --> 00:08:03,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Sidewinder Chief Mechanic - Kubo Eiji</b></font>

125
00:08:03,764 --> 00:08:07,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Racing Team Katagiri Street Version - </b></font>

126
00:08:03,764 --> 00:08:07,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Minagawa Hideo</b></font>

127
00:08:07,714 --> 00:08:11,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Team Spiral Leader - Ikeda Ryuji (Zero)</b></font>

128
00:08:11,774 --> 00:08:17,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll assemble a data collection team
and completely expose their strategy.</b></font>

129
00:08:17,314 --> 00:08:20,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let us take care of that.</b></font>

130
00:08:21,364 --> 00:08:25,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"If you know the enemy and know yourself,
you need not fear the result of a hundred battles."</b></font>

131
00:08:25,944 --> 00:08:29,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Information and data is
everything in today's racing.</b></font>

132
00:08:29,894 --> 00:08:33,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do we really have to go that far?</b></font>

133
00:08:33,364 --> 00:08:40,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think our opponent is good enough for the
best three in Kanagawa to sneak around like this.</b></font>

134
00:08:40,664 --> 00:08:44,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In any case, I'll settle this during my turn.</b></font>

135
00:08:45,204 --> 00:08:48,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, but you guys won't
have a chance to compete.</b></font>

136
00:08:48,794 --> 00:08:50,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You sound quite confident.</b></font>

137
00:08:50,624 --> 00:08:54,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Alright, I look forward to it, then.</b></font>

138
00:08:58,114 --> 00:09:04,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Team 246 Leader - Satoshi Omiya</b></font>

139
00:08:58,474 --> 00:09:04,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's quite an indirect and
hesitant strategy, isn't it?</b></font>

140
00:09:04,314 --> 00:09:09,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Team 246 Driver - Kobayakawa</b></font>

141
00:09:04,564 --> 00:09:06,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't like that sequence.</b></font>

142
00:09:06,694 --> 00:09:11,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sounds like the first team,
which is us, shouldn't win.</b></font>

143
00:09:13,564 --> 00:09:18,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, should we deliberately lose and
 let the next team take the credit?</b></font>

144
00:09:18,914 --> 00:09:21,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, please.</b></font>

145
00:09:21,274 --> 00:09:24,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A fair and square win is the best.</b></font>

146
00:09:24,614 --> 00:09:28,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm pissed at those Sidewinder guys, too.</b></font>

147
00:09:28,014 --> 00:09:31,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We didn't ask them to manage this.</b></font>

148
00:09:31,114 --> 00:09:34,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have no reason
to hold back for them.</b></font>

149
00:09:35,364 --> 00:09:37,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Show the true potential of 246.</b></font>

150
00:09:50,434 --> 00:09:51,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Amazing.</b></font>

151
00:09:51,904 --> 00:09:54,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She hits great distances without slicing.</b></font>

152
00:09:55,924 --> 00:09:57,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What happened, Mika?</b></font>

153
00:10:06,304 --> 00:10:08,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder what Takumi is doing now.</b></font>

154
00:10:10,994 --> 00:10:13,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Fujiwara, don't just space out.</b></font>

155
00:10:13,724 --> 00:10:15,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, I'm sorry.</b></font>

156
00:10:19,194 --> 00:10:20,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big news, Iketani!</b></font>

157
00:10:20,754 --> 00:10:22,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Check this out!</b></font>

158
00:10:22,814 --> 00:10:25,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}GOLF</b></font>

159
00:10:23,114 --> 00:10:24,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

160
00:10:24,094 --> 00:10:25,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A golf magazine?</b></font>

161
00:10:25,574 --> 00:10:27,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here, take a look inside.</b></font>

162
00:10:30,014 --> 00:10:31,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's her, right?</b></font>

163
00:10:31,964 --> 00:10:34,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"A new star in women's golf"</b></font>

164
00:10:34,694 --> 00:10:38,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Uehara Mika, seventeen years old"?!</b></font>

165
00:10:38,454 --> 00:10:41,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is the girl who slapped Takumi?</b></font>

166
00:10:41,364 --> 00:10:43,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm absolutely positive.</b></font>

167
00:10:43,184 --> 00:10:45,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She looked exactly like this.</b></font>

168
00:10:45,064 --> 00:10:50,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Man, if I'd known she was famous,
I would've asked for her autograph.</b></font>

169
00:10:50,344 --> 00:10:54,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A golf genius who hits
a white ball in the daylight</b></font>

170
00:10:54,664 --> 00:10:57,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and a driving genius who
tackles the roads at night.</b></font>

171
00:10:59,314 --> 00:11:03,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those are polar opposites, aren't they?</b></font>

172
00:11:03,664 --> 00:11:06,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if this romance
will develop any further.</b></font>

173
00:11:16,114 --> 00:11:18,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is downhill checkpoint 3.</b></font>

174
00:11:18,724 --> 00:11:20,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six just passed by.</b></font>

175
00:11:28,874 --> 00:11:32,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The FD just passed
hill climb checkpoint 7.</b></font>

176
00:11:41,234 --> 00:11:43,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How many years?</b></font>

177
00:11:43,074 --> 00:11:46,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's been a long time,
hasn't it, Takahashi Ryosuke?</b></font>

178
00:11:55,384 --> 00:11:58,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You seem to be having a hard time
because of the power increase.</b></font>

179
00:11:58,644 --> 00:12:00,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It can't be helped.</b></font>

180
00:12:00,314 --> 00:12:03,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, hill climbing is a power game.</b></font>

181
00:12:03,004 --> 00:12:05,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have something else that worries me.</b></font>

182
00:12:06,764 --> 00:12:10,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I saw some guys with stopwatches
scattered throughout the course.</b></font>

183
00:12:10,774 --> 00:12:13,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are they timing you?</b></font>

184
00:12:14,004 --> 00:12:15,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Probably.</b></font>

185
00:12:15,764 --> 00:12:18,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think it's pointless to check our times.</b></font>

186
00:12:19,424 --> 00:12:24,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're still setting up our cars, and
we haven't mastered the course yet.</b></font>

187
00:12:24,014 --> 00:12:26,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The speeds will be totally
different during the actual race.</b></font>

188
00:12:26,864 --> 00:12:30,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But it bothers me that they're
checking our times every so often.</b></font>

189
00:12:32,014 --> 00:12:33,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

190
00:12:33,014 --> 00:12:34,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's ready to go, Keisuke.</b></font>

191
00:12:35,214 --> 00:12:35,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

192
00:12:47,114 --> 00:12:50,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara seems to be in
good condition as usual.</b></font>

193
00:12:51,564 --> 00:12:55,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He appears to enjoy challenging
difficult courses like this.</b></font>

194
00:12:55,514 --> 00:13:00,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The car is tricky to drive in every
aspect, but he says it's easy.</b></font>

195
00:13:01,414 --> 00:13:04,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It makes me wonder if he's an alien.</b></font>

196
00:13:06,604 --> 00:13:08,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is this okay, Ryosuke?</b></font>

197
00:13:08,924 --> 00:13:14,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure an organized data collection
team is all over the course.</b></font>

198
00:13:16,444 --> 00:13:19,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our cars pace will pick up in the later half.</b></font>

199
00:13:19,414 --> 00:13:25,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyone with a trained eye will be able to accurately measure our potential.</b></font>

200
00:13:25,054 --> 00:13:26,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Probably so.</b></font>

201
00:13:26,804 --> 00:13:29,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shouldn't we think about using
some kind of camouflage?</b></font>

202
00:13:29,984 --> 00:13:33,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I'd rather not use any cheap tricks.</b></font>

203
00:13:33,024 --> 00:13:35,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If they want data, they can
have it, for today that is.</b></font>

204
00:13:37,664 --> 00:13:39,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry, Fumihiro.</b></font>

205
00:13:39,804 --> 00:13:42,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I made my decision after careful thinking.</b></font>

206
00:13:42,694 --> 00:13:49,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One thing I can say is that the people
collecting data aren't our next opponents.</b></font>

207
00:13:50,374 --> 00:13:51,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that so?</b></font>

208
00:13:52,144 --> 00:13:53,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Think about it.</b></font>

209
00:13:53,634 --> 00:13:54,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The battle is tomorrow.</b></font>

210
00:13:56,014 --> 00:13:59,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no time to set up
a car based on today's data.</b></font>

211
00:14:00,084 --> 00:14:02,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're right.</b></font>

212
00:14:02,154 --> 00:14:05,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They must be an opponent
we're racing against much later.</b></font>

213
00:14:05,094 --> 00:14:09,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If so, we still have time.</b></font>

214
00:14:09,414 --> 00:14:12,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We must focus on the opponent before us.</b></font>

215
00:14:22,564 --> 00:14:25,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The first half is a series of steep uphill slopes.</b></font>

216
00:14:25,664 --> 00:14:28,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The second half is a continuous mild slope.</b></font>

217
00:14:28,234 --> 00:14:31,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, that's from the
hill-climbing perspective, so...</b></font>

218
00:14:31,014 --> 00:14:33,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the opposite on the downhill.</b></font>

219
00:14:33,004 --> 00:14:34,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

220
00:14:34,314 --> 00:14:37,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But whether it's a hill-climb or downhill</b></font>

221
00:14:37,454 --> 00:14:42,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the key to this course are the parts
 where the road width suddenly changes.</b></font>

222
00:14:44,564 --> 00:14:50,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There are many places where two lanes change into one throughout the course.</b></font>

223
00:14:53,294 --> 00:14:56,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those will be important overtaking points.</b></font>

224
00:14:57,494 --> 00:14:58,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're right.</b></font>

225
00:14:58,924 --> 00:15:03,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know that in my head</b></font>

226
00:15:03,254 --> 00:15:11,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but the locals must know how to benefit from it, and they won't drive on the unfavorable side.</b></font>

227
00:15:11,784 --> 00:15:15,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And if you aim for it, 
you might fall into a trap.</b></font>

228
00:15:23,194 --> 00:15:26,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh man, a Lan Evo again</b></font>

229
00:15:26,824 --> 00:15:30,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How come my opponents always
seem to be driving 4WD cars?</b></font>

230
00:15:30,194 --> 00:15:31,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've had enough.</b></font>

231
00:15:31,694 --> 00:15:35,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why don't you claim to 
be Akagi's Lan Evo killer?</b></font>

232
00:15:35,474 --> 00:15:37,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That doesn't even make a good joke.</b></font>

233
00:15:37,574 --> 00:15:40,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can say that,
because you aren't driving.</b></font>

234
00:15:41,514 --> 00:15:46,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Frankly speaking, it's the car I hate to compete against the most on the mountain passes now.</b></font>

235
00:15:46,554 --> 00:15:48,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because it's absurdly fast.</b></font>

236
00:15:52,444 --> 00:15:56,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They gave us the choice of
being the leader or the pursuer.</b></font>

237
00:15:56,604 --> 00:15:58,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Which do you want, Kobayakawa?</b></font>

238
00:15:58,474 --> 00:16:04,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can be either, but I want to take
a close look at my opponent.</b></font>

239
00:16:04,764 --> 00:16:08,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think I'll be outrun by a 2WD car</b></font>

240
00:16:08,764 --> 00:16:13,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so the first race will be for recon,
and the second will be the real match.</b></font>

241
00:16:13,014 --> 00:16:14,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, we'll go with that, then.</b></font>

242
00:16:20,824 --> 00:16:21,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm Kobayakawa.</b></font>

243
00:16:22,664 --> 00:16:23,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm Takahashi Keisuke.</b></font>

244
00:16:39,074 --> 00:16:43,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since you're the leader, you know what to do without being told, don't you?</b></font>

245
00:16:44,304 --> 00:16:45,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know.</b></font>

246
00:16:45,824 --> 00:16:49,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Half of my job was finished yesterday.</b></font>

247
00:16:50,784 --> 00:16:53,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's what you wanted
to say, right, Brother?</b></font>

248
00:16:53,344 --> 00:16:54,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Correct.</b></font>

249
00:16:55,714 --> 00:16:56,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm counting on you.</b></font>

250
00:17:00,444 --> 00:17:01,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going to count down!</b></font>

251
00:17:02,344 --> 00:17:03,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five</b></font>

252
00:17:03,364 --> 00:17:04,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Four</b></font>

253
00:17:04,264 --> 00:17:05,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Three</b></font>

254
00:17:05,344 --> 00:17:06,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Two</b></font>

255
00:17:06,294 --> 00:17:07,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One</b></font>

256
00:17:07,344 --> 00:17:08,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

257
00:17:24,944 --> 00:17:29,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Give me your best prediction
on how this battle will unfold.</b></font>

258
00:17:30,664 --> 00:17:32,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Best prediction?</b></font>

259
00:17:32,854 --> 00:17:35,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's tough at the moment.</b></font>

260
00:17:38,204 --> 00:17:39,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's got power.</b></font>

261
00:17:39,814 --> 00:17:40,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Footwork's good, too.</b></font>

262
00:17:43,414 --> 00:17:48,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But the road will soon
become steep and rough.</b></font>

263
00:17:49,874 --> 00:17:52,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm curious as to how he'll handle it.</b></font>

264
00:17:56,344 --> 00:17:59,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know you don't have enough data.</b></font>

265
00:17:59,104 --> 00:18:02,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why I said "prediction."</b></font>

266
00:18:02,494 --> 00:18:06,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once you have data, you're
correct 100% of the time.</b></font>

267
00:18:12,014 --> 00:18:15,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The road suddenly widens here, but it'll narrow soon.</b></font>

268
00:18:16,594 --> 00:18:19,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well then, let me give you my prediction.</b></font>

269
00:18:20,854 --> 00:18:22,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just a prediction, okay?</b></font>

270
00:18:25,754 --> 00:18:27,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is my prediction.</b></font>

271
00:18:30,144 --> 00:18:31,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Amazing.</b></font>

272
00:18:31,774 --> 00:18:36,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's rare to see a rear-wheel-drive
car climbing the hill so sharply.</b></font>

273
00:18:37,164 --> 00:18:39,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But something's not right.</b></font>

274
00:18:40,404 --> 00:18:43,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't like the fact that the
car's behaving as it should.</b></font>

275
00:18:43,724 --> 00:18:46,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't feel any "plus factors."</b></font>

276
00:18:47,314 --> 00:18:50,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The driver's presence is too weak.</b></font>

277
00:18:52,414 --> 00:18:57,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're a fast driver, but still,
you're boring, Takahashi Keisuke.</b></font>

278
00:19:02,114 --> 00:19:06,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Omiya, what do you think
about Kobayakawa's decision?</b></font>

279
00:19:06,454 --> 00:19:10,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think his choice to be the 
pursuer for the first run is correct.</b></font>

280
00:19:10,344 --> 00:19:12,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Also, the road is very narrow.</b></font>

281
00:19:12,874 --> 00:19:17,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't see any disadvantage for
Kobayakawa, even if the race drags on.</b></font>

282
00:19:17,094 --> 00:19:23,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he can figure out what makes him faster
and slower than his opponent in the first run</b></font>

283
00:19:23,764 --> 00:19:26,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he can make a bold decisive
maneuver in the second run.</b></font>

284
00:19:37,514 --> 00:19:40,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you going to use the
same strategy, Omiya?</b></font>

285
00:19:40,634 --> 00:19:42,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know.</b></font>

286
00:19:42,364 --> 00:19:46,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll think about it after seeing
the results of the hill climb.</b></font>

287
00:19:46,844 --> 00:19:48,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Results?</b></font>

288
00:19:48,454 --> 00:19:50,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But Kobayakawa has an
absolute advantage, right?</b></font>

289
00:19:50,874 --> 00:19:52,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His opponent is an FD.</b></font>

290
00:19:52,864 --> 00:19:56,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't like it when I have
an absolute advantage.</b></font>

291
00:19:56,704 --> 00:19:59,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You never know until it's over.</b></font>

292
00:20:02,404 --> 00:20:04,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's good.</b></font>

293
00:20:04,154 --> 00:20:07,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He doesn't show any wasteful 
wheel spin even on this rough surface.</b></font>

294
00:20:14,724 --> 00:20:19,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your perfectionism comes through loud and clear.</b></font>

295
00:20:19,024 --> 00:20:22,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But your "doing your job right"
gets on my nerves.</b></font>

296
00:20:25,644 --> 00:20:26,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got it.</b></font>

297
00:20:26,764 --> 00:20:28,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This's enough.</b></font>

298
00:20:28,624 --> 00:20:32,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not like your team has
outrageously skilled drivers.</b></font>

299
00:20:39,474 --> 00:20:46,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Lately, the conversations between you and Keisuke have the tendency to sound like Buddhist riddles.</b></font>

300
00:20:46,594 --> 00:20:52,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't understand what I'm hearing from
your side, like your advice before the start.</b></font>

301
00:20:52,614 --> 00:20:58,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What did Keisuke mean when he said
half of his job was finished yesterday?</b></font>

302
00:20:59,764 --> 00:21:01,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, it's nothing.</b></font>

303
00:21:01,474 --> 00:21:04,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It doesn't have any complicated meaning.</b></font>

304
00:21:04,114 --> 00:21:08,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you live with someone under the same roof, you can communicate without saying much.</b></font>

305
00:21:13,544 --> 00:21:18,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In principle, we've agreed to finish the race
quickly whenever we start in the lead position.</b></font>

306
00:21:19,584 --> 00:21:26,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The first half of this course is made of steep hills, so he
must preserve his tires while the FD is at a disadvantage.</b></font>

307
00:21:27,704 --> 00:21:34,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then he can execute a super attack by making the best use
 of his tires in several high-speed sections on the second half.</b></font>

308
00:21:35,514 --> 00:21:37,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Halfway there.</b></font>

309
00:21:37,284 --> 00:21:40,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The slope will be milder
compared to the first half.</b></font>

310
00:21:40,114 --> 00:21:41,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He'll make a move somewhere.</b></font>

311
00:21:41,414 --> 00:21:42,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where will it be?</b></font>

312
00:21:43,464 --> 00:21:47,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the kind of simple and easy strategy that Keisuke would prefer, right?</b></font>

313
00:21:47,744 --> 00:21:52,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's obvious he'll lose his edge if he
challenges the Lan Evo to a long race.</b></font>

314
00:21:53,814 --> 00:21:58,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The key to victory is how much
more Keisuke can raise his top speed.</b></font>

315
00:22:00,644 --> 00:22:05,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's what he meant when he said half of his job was finished during yesterday's practice.</b></font>

316
00:22:09,434 --> 00:22:11,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where, dammit?</b></font>

317
00:22:11,724 --> 00:22:13,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where are you going
to make your move?</b></font>

318
00:22:16,684 --> 00:22:18,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know your strategy.</b></font>

319
00:22:18,784 --> 00:22:21,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When it comes to rapid acceleration, the Evo won't lose to any other car.</b></font>

320
00:22:22,514 --> 00:22:25,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The rest is a matter of concentration.</b></font>

321
00:22:27,364 --> 00:22:29,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a match of concentration.</b></font>

322
00:22:29,944 --> 00:22:32,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One small mistake will cost you the match.</b></font>

323
00:22:35,294 --> 00:22:37,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The road's going to widen starting here.</b></font>

324
00:22:37,474 --> 00:22:39,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It must be around here.</b></font>

325
00:22:39,264 --> 00:22:40,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here?</b></font>

326
00:22:40,814 --> 00:22:41,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Should I try?</b></font>

327
00:22:43,014 --> 00:22:47,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Evo and Imp drivers 
religiously believe in an idea.</b></font>

328
00:22:50,014 --> 00:22:55,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That cars developed for rallying must
be the best on the public streets.</b></font>

329
00:22:59,394 --> 00:23:00,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Last spurt yet?</b></font>

330
00:23:02,204 --> 00:23:03,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, he hasn't.</b></font>

331
00:23:03,334 --> 00:23:04,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not yet.</b></font>

332
00:23:04,394 --> 00:23:05,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not here.</b></font>

333
00:23:05,664 --> 00:23:06,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe the next?</b></font>

334
00:23:07,724 --> 00:23:09,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where is it, dammit?</b></font>

335
00:23:11,504 --> 00:23:17,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But rallies were originally
done in snow or on dirt.</b></font>

336
00:23:17,164 --> 00:23:22,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>4WDs aren't necessarily
unbeatable on dry asphalt.</b></font>

337
00:23:23,814 --> 00:23:26,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why I predict</b></font>

338
00:23:27,084 --> 00:23:30,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>this race will be decided
uneventfully in the first run.</b></font>

339
00:23:33,664 --> 00:23:37,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The road just got narrower,
and the visibility is poor.</b></font>

340
00:23:37,414 --> 00:23:38,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You won't be able to keep this pace up.</b></font>

341
00:23:40,914 --> 00:23:47,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just before the goal, about 2 to 3 minutes in 
terms of time, his concentration will reach its peak.</b></font>

342
00:23:47,414 --> 00:23:53,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If our opponent can keep up with
Keisuke's top speed, Keisuke will lose.</b></font>

343
00:23:55,454 --> 00:23:56,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The winner will be...</b></font>

344
00:24:07,014 --> 00:24:08,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You won't get away!</b></font>

345
00:24:08,514 --> 00:24:10,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Evo, let's do it!</b></font>

346
00:24:20,814 --> 00:24:23,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He caught me off guard, 
sprinting out in a place like that.</b></font>

347
00:24:25,084 --> 00:24:28,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Public roads are unfair in every way.</b></font>

348
00:24:31,774 --> 00:24:36,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On a complex winding road 
layout with no escape zones</b></font>

349
00:24:36,514 --> 00:24:39,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>strictly speaking, you can
never reach the limit.</b></font>

350
00:24:40,914 --> 00:24:46,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If there was a public road specialist,
that person would possess</b></font>

351
00:24:46,114 --> 00:24:52,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>courage, fighting spirit, experience, and 
in some cases, the recklessness of youth.</b></font>

352
00:24:55,944 --> 00:24:56,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can catch up.</b></font>

353
00:24:56,954 --> 00:24:58,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I must.</b></font>

354
00:24:58,634 --> 00:25:02,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I must catch him once
again no matter what!</b></font>

355
00:25:03,284 --> 00:25:08,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and a plus factor given only
to those chosen by God.</b></font>

356
00:25:32,914 --> 00:25:36,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Following the brake light of the front car.</b></font>

357
00:25:36,604 --> 00:25:42,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A shimmering light up ahead in the dark street.</b></font>

358
00:25:42,794 --> 00:25:46,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the silence like a silent film.</b></font>

359
00:25:46,444 --> 00:25:52,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The light was all I could depend on.</b></font>

360
00:25:53,164 --> 00:25:58,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I felt like I could catch it,</b></font>

361
00:25:58,244 --> 00:26:01,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>if I passed through this tree-lined street.</b></font>

362
00:26:01,774 --> 00:26:05,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Get up! I just can't understand.</b></font>

363
00:26:05,414 --> 00:26:11,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I couldn't find what I'd been looking for.</b></font>

364
00:26:11,864 --> 00:26:15,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, it starts at this moment.</b></font>

365
00:26:15,354 --> 00:26:19,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At this place.</b></font>

366
00:26:19,024 --> 00:26:22,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please turn over the flyleaf.</b></font>

367
00:26:28,644 --> 00:26:32,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I lost my way.</b></font>

368
00:26:32,254 --> 00:26:35,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fogged up windows, and</b></font>

369
00:26:35,314 --> 00:26:38,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>messed up navigation.</b></font>

370
00:26:38,654 --> 00:26:42,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As the stoplight turns red</b></font>

371
00:26:42,314 --> 00:26:48,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>a light in the side mirror blinds my eyes.</b></font>

372
00:26:48,984 --> 00:26:54,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I gradually close the window</b></font>

373
00:26:54,024 --> 00:26:57,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to stop the cold wind from blowing in.</b></font>

374
00:26:57,454 --> 00:27:01,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Get up! I just can't understand.</b></font>

375
00:27:01,194 --> 00:27:07,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We must choose one of the paths that lie ahead.</b></font>

376
00:27:07,564 --> 00:27:10,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, it starts at this moment.</b></font>

377
00:27:10,984 --> 00:27:14,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because you're with me.</b></font>

378
00:27:14,604 --> 00:27:17,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please turn over the flyleaf.</b></font>

